      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is a practical opportunity for a buyer seeking affordable transportation, a project car, or a dependable parts donor. It shows the wear you would expect from an older used vehicle, but it still offers solid value for the price and a straightforward ownership proposition. Priced to sell, this is a cost-conscious way to get behind the wheel without overextending your budget.",
