    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "If you\u2019re after simple, affordable wheels without spending a fortune, this one is worth a look. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it\u2019s a usable car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Great as a cheap runabout, first car, or little project for someone handy. Priced to make sense and sold with a straightforward, no-nonsense approach.",
