    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running used car with solid bones and real driver potential. Engine pulls cleanly, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels composed enough to enjoy as-is while you sort the cosmetic needs. Not a show car, but a straightforward, usable platform with plenty of life left for someone who wants affordable transportation, a budget build, or a hands-on project. Priced right for the condition and hard to beat for the money.",
