      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Turn heads without breaking the bank\u2014this car has the kind of well-lived character you can\u2019t fake. It\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly ride with plenty of story left to write, whether you need a practical around-town companion, a starter project, or something with personality that stands apart from the usual bland commuters. There\u2019s a rugged charm here that makes it easy to imagine bringing it back to its full shine, and at this price, it\u2019s a rare chance to get into something memorable for very little upfront.",
